      source: 'pragma solidity ^0.8.0;\n' +
        '\n' +
        'import "@openzeppelin/contracts/token/ERC20/ERC20.sol";\n' +
        'import "@openzeppelin/contracts/access/AccessControl.sol";\n' +
        '\n' +
        'contract Capyswap is ERC20, AccessControl {\n' +
        '   bytes32 public constant MINTER_ROLE = keccak256("MINTER_ROLE");\n' +
        '\n' +
        '   constructor(\n' +
        '        string memory name,\n' +
        '        string memory symbol,\n' +
        '        uint256 initialSupply) ERC20(name, symbol) {\n' +
        '      _mint(msg.sender, initialSupply);\n' +
        '      _setupRole(DEFAULT_ADMIN_ROLE, msg.sender);\n' +
        '      _setRoleAdmin(MINTER_ROLE, DEFAULT_ADMIN_ROLE);\n' +
        '   }\n' +
        '\n' +
        '   event Debug(address user, address sender, bytes32 role, bytes32 adminRole, bytes32 senderRole);\n' +
        '   event ChecksoloAdmin(address user);\n' +
        '   event ChecksoloMinters(address user);\n' +
        '\n' +
        '   modifier soloAdmin() {\n' +
        '      emit ChecksoloAdmin(msg.sender);\n' +
        '      require(isAdmin(msg.sender), "Restricted to admins");\n' +
        '      _;\n' +
        '   }\n' +
        '\n' +
        '   modifier soloMinters() {\n' +
        '      emit ChecksoloMinters(msg.sender);\n' +
        '      require(isMinter(msg.sender), "Caller is not a minter");\n' +
        '      _;\n' +
        '   }\n' +
        '\n' +
        '   function isAdmin(address account) public virtual view returns (bool) {\n' +
        '      return hasRole(DEFAULT_ADMIN_ROLE, account);\n' +
        '   }\n' +
        '\n' +
        '   function isMinter(address account) public virtual view returns (bool) {\n' +
        '      return hasRole(MINTER_ROLE, account);\n' +
        '   }\n' +
        '\n' +
        '   function mint(address to, uint256 amount) public soloMinters {\n' +
        '      _mint(to, amount);\n' +
        '   }\n' +
        '\n' +
        '   function addMinterRole(address to) public soloAdmin {\n' +
        '      emit Debug(to, msg.sender, MINTER_ROLE, getRoleAdmin(MINTER_ROLE), DEFAULT_ADMIN_ROLE);\n' +
        '      grantRole(MINTER_ROLE, to);\n' +
        '   }\n' +
        '\n' +
        '   function removeMinterRole (address to) public {\n' +
        '      renounceRole(MINTER_ROLE, to);\n' +
        '   }\n' +
        '}\n',
